<v-container>
  <v-layout>
    <v-flex>
      <v-card>
        <v-card-text>
          <v-form ref="formLogin" @submit="login">
            <text-field
              label="User"
              v-model="user"
              :rules="[validations.required]"
              @keyup.enter="login"
            ></text-field>
            <v-text-field
              label="Password"
              v-model="password"
              type="password"
              :rules="[validations.required]"
              @keyup.enter="login"
            ></v-text-field>
          </v-form>
        </v-card-text>
        <v-card-actions>
          <v-btn color="primary" @click="login">Login</v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
      </v-card>
    </v-flex>
  </v-layout>
</v-container>
